body:
#### PR description:

This PR removes the plugin `HLTPFDiJetCorrCheckerWithDiTau`, which has been replaced by a copy of it named `HLTDiPFJetPlusTausCandidatePFJetProducer` (see #40993 and [CMSHLT-2700](https://its.cern.ch/jira/browse/CMSHLT-2700)). The `.cc` file is renamed accordingly.

Merely technical. No changes expected.

#### PR validation:

None.
